snippet.title: Code Alkonost | Official Sneak Peek Teaser | Survival Horror based on Slavic Mythology
snippet.description:
Code Alkonost is a first-person survival horror video game inspired by Slavic Mythology.
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2062030/Code_Alkonost_Awakening_of_Evil/
Gameplay showcase (exclusive demo, 10 minutes of gameplay): https://youtu.be/j69NryJJ1Tg
Website - https://codealkonost.com/

Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/codealkonost
Twitter - https://twitter.com/AlkonostCode
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/codealkonost/
Support on Patreon - https://www.patreon.com/codealkonost

Collaborators on the game teaser:
Voice Acting Studio SENSIBLE SHOUTING
Rusalka's voice in the video: Đurđina Radić (Djixx)
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/SenShout 
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/sensibleshouting/?hl=en 
Youtube - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5fps2BsdPaqvlACiKlX0nQ 
Linkedin - https://www.linkedin.com/company/senshout/

#slavicmythology #indiedev #videogames
